        <item>
            <title>Apple 静静删除 iPhone 16 镜头「抗反射镜头涂层」描述，网民实试相机拍强光仍有鬼影</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/26/iphone-16-anti-reflective-lens-coatng/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone-16-anti-reflective-lens-coatng</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/26/iphone-16-anti-reflective-lens-coatng/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 07:25:02 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 16]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 16 Plus]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 16 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 16 Pro Max]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1265492</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 先前在规格表中标明为 iPhone 16 系列增加了「抗反射镜头涂层」，以防止在光线复杂的环境下出现「鬼影」问题，惟现时却被网民发现 Apple 静静地删除了 iPhone 16 系列的后置镜头「抗反射镜头涂层」描述。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1265526 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240925at-694x395.png" alt="" width="694" height="395" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240925at-694x395.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240925at-1280x729.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Apple 静静地删除了 iPhone 16 系列的后置镜头「抗反射镜头涂层」描述（图片来源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/iphone/compare/?modelList=iphone-16-pro-max,iphone-16-pro,iphone-15-pro">Apple</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">据 MacRumors 论坛用户指，Apple 早前曾在 iPhone 16 系列的技术规格中提到「抗反射镜头涂层」，但这项描述已从 Apple 官网及 Apple Store 应用程式中被悄然移除。Apple 官网当时曾显示，iPhone 16 Pro 及 Pro Max 配备 「防反光镜头涂层」，而 iPhone16 及 16 Plus 则有「抗反射镜头涂层（融合式摄像头）」。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1265523 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/antireflectivelensis-1-423x580.png" alt="" width="423" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/antireflectivelensis-1-423x580.png 423w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/antireflectivelensis-1.png 656w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 423px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲MacRumors 论坛用户指原本 Apple 有列明 iPhone 16 系列有「抗反射镜头涂层」（Anti-reflective lens coating）（图片来源：<a href="https://forums.macrumors.com/threads/anti-reflective-lens-coating-gone-from-16-line-ups-tech-spec.2437703/">MacRumors</a>）</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1265522 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/cms_2024092215553443-573x580.jpg" alt="" width="573" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/cms_2024092215553443-573x580.jpg 573w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/cms_2024092215553443.jpg 870w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 573px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Apple 官网曾显示 iPhone 16 Pro 系列配备 「防反光镜头涂层」，iPhone 16 系列则有「抗反射镜头涂层（融合式摄像头）」（图片来源：<a href="https://longportapp.com/zh-HK/news/214870749">LONGPORT</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">抗反射镜头涂层技术是透过减少光线在镜头表面反射，从而提升成像清晰度及色彩还原度。但从中国网民实际测试结果来看，iPhone 16 在拍摄强光源或复杂光源环境下的物体时，眩光现象依旧明显。据新浪科技猜测，Apple 有可能避免宣传不实而引起争议。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1265529 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240925at-1-1-694x386.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240925at-1-1-694x386.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240925at-1-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中国网民实际测试结果来看，似乎依旧有鬼影</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://forums.macrumors.com/threads/anti-reflective-lens-coating-gone-from-16-line-ups-tech-spec.2437703/">MacRumors</a>、<a href="https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2024/09/apple-debuts-iphone-16-pro-and-iphone-16-pro-max/">Apple</a>、<a href="https://longportapp.com/zh-HK/news/214870749">LONGPORT</a>、<a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/discovery/2024-09-23/doc-incqawwc2141827.shtml">新浪科技</a>、<a href="https://new.qq.com/rain/a/20240924A03C6900">腾讯网</a>、<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/iphone/compare/?modelList=iphone-16-pro-max,iphone-16-pro,iphone-15-pro">Apple</a>、<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/794/711.htm">IT 之家</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/20/iphone-16-pro-iphone-16/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】iPhone 16 / 16 Pro   新实体影相按钮 + 大量新相机镜头试相 + 无线充电实试</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/18/iphone16proreview/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPhone 16 Pro Max 详细开箱影片，并非只「多了颗掣」</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/10/iphone-16-%e7%b3%bb%e5%88%97-pro-max-%e5%a4%96%e5%aa%92%e4%b8%8a%e6%89%8b%e8%a9%95%e6%b8%ac-%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e6%9c%80%e6%84%9b-18-%e5%80%8b%e5%8a%9f%e8%83%bd-apple-watch-s10-%e5%8f%8a-airpods-4/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPhone 16 系列 Pro Max 外媒上手评测，港人最爱 18 个功能</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/26/iphone-16-anti-reflective-lens-coatng/mobile-phone/">Apple 静静删除 iPhone 16 镜头「抗反射镜头涂层」描述，网民实试相机拍强光仍有鬼影</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
