        <item>
            <title>可捉芒亨魔物的数码暴龙机　Monster Hunter 20 周年最新联乘产品</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/26/monster-huntert-20th-x-digimon/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=monster-huntert-20th-x-digimon</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/26/monster-huntert-20th-x-digimon/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 06:45:21 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[monster hunter]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[数码暴龙]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1265608</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今年是 Monster Hunter 推出 20 周年，今日（26 日）BANDAI 在日本购物网站 Premium Bandai 推出「数码暴龙 COLOR 魔物猎人 20 周年纪念版」，即日起在日本开放预购，香港的玩家可能要稍等一阵。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265615" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/459163799_8455793810-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/459163799_8455793810-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/459163799_8455793810.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/459163799_8455793810-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有「雄火龙」和「雷狼龙」两种配色可选</p><div>为纪念《Monster Hunter》系列 20 周年，BANDAI 推出了「数码暴龙 COLOR 魔物猎人 20 周年纪念版」，提供「雄火龙」和「雷狼龙」两种配色，内置彩色萤幕，可随心更换背景，使用随附的 USB-C 线即可充电。最重要的是，这款 20 周年纪念版可以和过去全部 COLOR 系列对战。</div><div></div><div><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265616" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/1000215405_1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/1000215405_1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/1000215405_1.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/1000215405_1-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></div><div style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://p-bandai.jp/item/item-1000215405/">P-BANDAI.jp</a></div><div></div><div></div><div>是次推出的 20 周年 COLOR 游戏机收录了 36 只魔物，暂时可见有火龙、雷狼龙、泡狐龙、金狮子、奇怪龙、迅龙、黑蚀龙、轰龙，以及今次原创的火龙暴龙兽及雷狼龙加鲁鲁兽。另外亦设有火山、沙漠、雪山、塔等背景图案供用家自由切换。</div><div></div><div><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265610" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460660914_2044866779-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460660914_2044866779-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460660914_2044866779.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460660914_2044866779-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></div><div></div><div style="text-align: center;">▲除了一般魔物，更收录了亚种，合共全 36 种魔物</div><div></div><div></div><div><div>今次更特地邀请了《数码暴龙》角色设计担当渡边けんじ绘制联乘魔物：雄火龙结合暴龙兽的「レウスグレイモン（火龙暴龙兽）」及雷狼龙结合加鲁鲁兽的「ジンオウガルルモン（雷狼龙加鲁鲁兽）」 ，2 款均为可培育魔物。</div><div></div><div></div></div><div><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265611" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/461148042_1223380178-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/461148042_1223380178-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/461148042_1223380178.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/461148042_1223380178-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></div><div></div><div style="text-align: center;">▲渡边けんじ全新绘制，原创的火龙暴龙兽及雷狼龙加鲁鲁兽</div><div></div><p>与过去 COLOR 系列相同，玩家在「冷却模式」时可暂停饥饿、力量值下降。此外，玩家可备份保存魔物。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265612" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460321421_5449507380-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460321421_5449507380-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460321421_5449507380.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460321421_5449507380-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265613" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/459266790_1573947529-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024