            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1265627</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今日东京电玩展（TGS）首日开放传媒、商业机构率先入场，而在昨晚《人中之龙 8 外传 Pirates in Hawaii》开发商 SEGA 就搞了一场盛大派对，unwire 现场记者亦有入场观看，重点当然是「港区女子」获选者有到现场同传媒一齐玩！之后到今日 SEGA 亦有在会场内提供游戏试玩。等我们记者在现场为大家报道。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265651" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1530-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1530-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1530.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265656" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1494-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1494-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_1494.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265647" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0720-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0720-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0720.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>SEGA 在昨晚搞了一场「SEGA TGS Pre Party」邀请传媒、KOL 到场一齐狂欢。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265653" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0759-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0759-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0759.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265650" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0703-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0703-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0703.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《人中之龙 8 外传 Pirates in Hawaii》游戏里面会出现，早前在审查中突为而出的「港区女子」的其中 3 位也有登场。赛车女郎雾岛圣子、Coser 澁谷果歩、游戏直播主 Misoshiru 有到现场，大晒肌肉。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1265648" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0686-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="800" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0686-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0686-rotated.jpg 506w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 450px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265649" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0679-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0679-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0679.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265655" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0651-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0651-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0651.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265657" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0637-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0637-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0637.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>到今日（26 日）开场，SEGA 摊位亦正式开幕，里面最大区域当然是《人中之龙 8 外传 Pirates in Hawaii》试玩，即使今日是 TGS 商务日但现场排队试玩的人龙，目视应该是全场数一数二最长！</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265629" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460283125_1309418937-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460283125_1309418937-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460283125_1309418937-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p>SEGA 今年在 TGS 里面提供的《人中之龙 8 外传 Pirates in Hawaii》试玩内容，由真岛吾朗与诺亚在登陆夏威夷开始。在海滩上试玩真岛的两种战斗方式，狂犬 Style 与海盗 Style。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265641" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0023-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0023-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0023.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265642" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0027-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0027-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0027.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>狂犬 Style 利用了真岛最在行的速度战斗，以拳脚、小刀攻击，另外打击敌人飞天后，可跳上空中漂浮对敌人施展追击，在空中展开不同技法。在这个 Style 里面可储「狂气计」，储满后可发动「分身」攻击，在分身途中真岛本人更可施展回转攻击等特殊技。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265638" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0014-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0014-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0014.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265637" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0022-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0022-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0022.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265643" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0016-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0016-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0016.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>海盗 Style 则是攻击范围广阔的攻击，真岛可用上 3 种不同的海贼道具「手枪」「回力镖」「二刀流刀剑」，切换这些道具进行近接、远隔打击。当然海盗 Style 也可滞空进行追击。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265639" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0010-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0010-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0010.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265633" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0004-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0004-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0004.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265634" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0007-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0007-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0007.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在现场也可试玩最新游戏热点，包括卡拉 OK、疯狂送外卖、龙赛车，还有换装等等。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265640" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0029-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0029-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0029.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265630" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0028-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0028-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0028.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265632" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0003-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0003-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0003.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265631" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0002-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0002-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0002.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>试玩版还包括了登陆疯狂兰提斯的情景。今次试玩报道到此，期待日后 SEGA 有更多新资料公开。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265636" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0026-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0026-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0026.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265635" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0019-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0019-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/piratesinhawaii0019.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1265659" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0719-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0719-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0719.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/26/sega-tgs/game-channel/">【TGS 2024】SEGA TGS 派对美女如云  《人中之龙 8 外传》试玩</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
