        </item>
        <item>
            <title>女监考员承认上载文凭试试题至小红书，涉违反保密协议还押候判</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/25/dse-2024/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=dse-2024</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/25/dse-2024/life-tech/social-network/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 14:19:19 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交网络]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[dse]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小红书]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[文凭试]]>
